[
    {
        "text": "this episode was filmed on october 16",
        "start": 0.08,
        "duration": 4.4
    },
    {
        "text": "2020. you can find our most recent",
        "start": 2.48,
        "duration": 3.52
    },
    {
        "text": "information on the pandemic in the",
        "start": 4.48,
        "duration": 4.31
    },
    {
        "text": "playlist linked in the description",
        "start": 6.0,
        "duration": 5.04
    },
    {
        "text": "[Music]",
        "start": 8.79,
        "duration": 4.009
    },
    {
        "text": "although we tend to think of covet 19",
        "start": 11.04,
        "duration": 3.679
    },
    {
        "text": "primarily as a lung infection",
        "start": 12.799,
        "duration": 3.521
    },
    {
        "text": "more and more evidence suggests that we",
        "start": 14.719,
        "duration": 3.761
    },
    {
        "text": "should also be looking out for its toll",
        "start": 16.32,
        "duration": 3.92
    },
    {
        "text": "on the heart around the world doctors",
        "start": 18.48,
        "duration": 3.36
    },
    {
        "text": "have noticed a number of different heart",
        "start": 20.24,
        "duration": 3.6
    },
    {
        "text": "problems in some people with kovid",
        "start": 21.84,
        "duration": 3.92
    },
    {
        "text": "including muscle damage inflammation",
        "start": 23.84,
        "duration": 4.08
    },
    {
        "text": "abnormal heartbeats and blood clots",
        "start": 25.76,
        "duration": 4.08
    },
    {
        "text": "in fact one report from back in may",
        "start": 27.92,
        "duration": 4.319
    },
    {
        "text": "estimated that between 7 and 17 percent",
        "start": 29.84,
        "duration": 3.28
    },
    {
        "text": "of patients",
        "start": 32.239,
        "duration": 3.681
    },
    {
        "text": "hospitalized for coven 19 had injury to",
        "start": 33.12,
        "duration": 3.439
    },
    {
        "text": "their hearts",
        "start": 35.92,
        "duration": 2.56
    },
    {
        "text": "and it may be common in cases outside",
        "start": 36.559,
        "duration": 3.84
    },
    {
        "text": "the hospital too even those we think of",
        "start": 38.48,
        "duration": 3.84
    },
    {
        "text": "as some of the most physically healthy",
        "start": 40.399,
        "duration": 4.16
    },
    {
        "text": "like professional athletes may be at",
        "start": 42.32,
        "duration": 4.16
    },
    {
        "text": "risk so scientists are paying attention",
        "start": 44.559,
        "duration": 2.48
    },
    {
        "text": "to this",
        "start": 46.48,
        "duration": 2.079
    },
    {
        "text": "because the better we can understand how",
        "start": 47.039,
        "duration": 3.52
    },
    {
        "text": "covet affects the heart the better we",
        "start": 48.559,
        "duration": 2.561
    },
    {
        "text": "can avoid",
        "start": 50.559,
        "duration": 2.561
    },
    {
        "text": "unexpected consequences down the road",
        "start": 51.12,
        "duration": 3.759
    },
    {
        "text": "there's one condition in particular",
        "start": 53.12,
        "duration": 3.759
    },
    {
        "text": "that's drawn a fair amount of attention",
        "start": 54.879,
        "duration": 2.601
    },
    {
        "text": "it's called",
        "start": 56.879,
        "duration": 2.961
    },
    {
        "text": "myocarditis and it's a general term for",
        "start": 57.48,
        "duration": 3.879
    },
    {
        "text": "inflammation of the heart muscle",
        "start": 59.84,
        "duration": 3.44
    },
    {
        "text": "it's often due to viral infection like",
        "start": 61.359,
        "duration": 4.321
    },
    {
        "text": "an adenovirus or rubella these viruses",
        "start": 63.28,
        "duration": 4.4
    },
    {
        "text": "can directly infect heart muscle cells",
        "start": 65.68,
        "duration": 3.92
    },
    {
        "text": "damaging them and using them to create",
        "start": 67.68,
        "duration": 4.08
    },
    {
        "text": "more viruses this can cause inflammation",
        "start": 69.6,
        "duration": 3.68
    },
    {
        "text": "and about one percent of the people",
        "start": 71.76,
        "duration": 3.359
    },
    {
        "text": "hospitalized due to acute viral",
        "start": 73.28,
        "duration": 4.159
    },
    {
        "text": "infections have heart injury and based",
        "start": 75.119,
        "duration": 3.441
    },
    {
        "text": "on the evidence we have",
        "start": 77.439,
        "duration": 3.601
    },
    {
        "text": "it looks like sars cov2 the virus that",
        "start": 78.56,
        "duration": 4.0
    },
    {
        "text": "causes coven 19",
        "start": 81.04,
        "duration": 3.68
    },
    {
        "text": "can infect heart tissue as well though",
        "start": 82.56,
        "duration": 3.919
    },
    {
        "text": "it's not clear if it's the muscle cells",
        "start": 84.72,
        "duration": 3.92
    },
    {
        "text": "themselves or other nearby parts",
        "start": 86.479,
        "duration": 4.081
    },
    {
        "text": "whatever virus causes the infection the",
        "start": 88.64,
        "duration": 3.68
    },
    {
        "text": "immune system responds and it can",
        "start": 90.56,
        "duration": 3.44
    },
    {
        "text": "sometimes help prevent the virus from",
        "start": 92.32,
        "duration": 3.52
    },
    {
        "text": "doing damage but this can actually",
        "start": 94.0,
        "duration": 4.159
    },
    {
        "text": "also cause myocarditis because by",
        "start": 95.84,
        "duration": 4.4
    },
    {
        "text": "fighting the virus so hard the immune",
        "start": 98.159,
        "duration": 4.24
    },
    {
        "text": "system itself can end up inflaming the",
        "start": 100.24,
        "duration": 2.8
    },
    {
        "text": "heart and",
        "start": 102.399,
        "duration": 2.881
    },
    {
        "text": "however it happens this inflammation can",
        "start": 103.04,
        "duration": 3.039
    },
    {
        "text": "cause trouble",
        "start": 105.28,
        "duration": 2.479
    },
    {
        "text": "for instance inflammation can make the",
        "start": 106.079,
        "duration": 3.441
    },
    {
        "text": "heart larger and being big",
        "start": 107.759,
        "duration": 3.921
    },
    {
        "text": "also makes the heart weaker so it has to",
        "start": 109.52,
        "duration": 3.68
    },
    {
        "text": "work harder to move blood around a",
        "start": 111.68,
        "duration": 2.399
    },
    {
        "text": "person's body",
        "start": 113.2,
        "duration": 2.559
    },
    {
        "text": "and it can also cause the heart to build",
        "start": 114.079,
        "duration": 3.521
    },
    {
        "text": "up what's essentially a bunch of scar",
        "start": 115.759,
        "duration": 2.32
    },
    {
        "text": "tissue",
        "start": 117.6,
        "duration": 2.24
    },
    {
        "text": "down the line these effects can mess up",
        "start": 118.079,
        "duration": 3.36
    },
    {
        "text": "the heart's muscle and electrical",
        "start": 119.84,
        "duration": 3.2
    },
    {
        "text": "systems and lead to serious",
        "start": 121.439,
        "duration": 3.04
    },
    {
        "text": "life-threatening conditions like",
        "start": 123.04,
        "duration": 3.6
    },
    {
        "text": "abnormal heartbeats or arrhythmias they",
        "start": 124.479,
        "duration": 3.521
    },
    {
        "text": "can also cause blood clots",
        "start": 126.64,
        "duration": 3.679
    },
    {
        "text": "if stagnant blood pools in the heart",
        "start": 128.0,
        "duration": 4.0
    },
    {
        "text": "that raises the risk of strokes and",
        "start": 130.319,
        "duration": 2.721
    },
    {
        "text": "cardiac arrest",
        "start": 132.0,
        "duration": 2.72
    },
    {
        "text": "and even heart failure which happens",
        "start": 133.04,
        "duration": 3.44
    },
    {
        "text": "when the heart simply can't pump enough",
        "start": 134.72,
        "duration": 3.28
    },
    {
        "text": "blood so scientists and doctors are",
        "start": 136.48,
        "duration": 2.96
    },
    {
        "text": "working really hard to understand",
        "start": 138.0,
        "duration": 3.36
    },
    {
        "text": "how and when all this happens so they",
        "start": 139.44,
        "duration": 3.92
    },
    {
        "text": "can better look out for it unfortunately",
        "start": 141.36,
        "duration": 3.36
    },
    {
        "text": "though all this might be happening",
        "start": 143.36,
        "duration": 3.36
    },
    {
        "text": "without the person realizing it see",
        "start": 144.72,
        "duration": 4.32
    },
    {
        "text": "myocarditis itself doesn't necessarily",
        "start": 146.72,
        "duration": 3.2
    },
    {
        "text": "feel like anything",
        "start": 149.04,
        "duration": 2.8
    },
    {
        "text": "many people don't feel symptoms at all",
        "start": 149.92,
        "duration": 3.679
    },
    {
        "text": "and only become aware of it when heart",
        "start": 151.84,
        "duration": 2.88
    },
    {
        "text": "failure occurs",
        "start": 153.599,
        "duration": 2.881
    },
    {
        "text": "even if symptoms do occur they're",
        "start": 154.72,
        "duration": 3.519
    },
    {
        "text": "generally kind of vague things like",
        "start": 156.48,
        "duration": 2.32
    },
    {
        "text": "fatigue",
        "start": 158.239,
        "duration": 2.481
    },
    {
        "text": "shortness of breath chest pain or heart",
        "start": 158.8,
        "duration": 3.12
    },
    {
        "text": "palpitations so",
        "start": 160.72,
        "duration": 2.96
    },
    {
        "text": "it's hard to know what they're from and",
        "start": 161.92,
        "duration": 3.28
    },
    {
        "text": "heart problems don't just happen",
        "start": 163.68,
        "duration": 3.6
    },
    {
        "text": "in severe or even current cases of",
        "start": 165.2,
        "duration": 4.0
    },
    {
        "text": "kovitz a study that did mris on the",
        "start": 167.28,
        "duration": 4.239
    },
    {
        "text": "hearts of 26 coveted positive athletes",
        "start": 169.2,
        "duration": 4.48
    },
    {
        "text": "found evidence of heart inflammation in",
        "start": 171.519,
        "duration": 2.72
    },
    {
        "text": "four",
        "start": 173.68,
        "duration": 2.559
    },
    {
        "text": "who'd either had mild symptoms or no",
        "start": 174.239,
        "duration": 3.92
    },
    {
        "text": "symptoms at all meanwhile a study from",
        "start": 176.239,
        "duration": 3.681
    },
    {
        "text": "germany found that of a hundred people",
        "start": 178.159,
        "duration": 3.601
    },
    {
        "text": "diagnosed with coping 19",
        "start": 179.92,
        "duration": 4.399
    },
    {
        "text": "60 percent had heart inflammation and",
        "start": 181.76,
        "duration": 4.32
    },
    {
        "text": "there didn't seem to be any relationship",
        "start": 184.319,
        "duration": 2.401
    },
    {
        "text": "between that",
        "start": 186.08,
        "duration": 2.48
    },
    {
        "text": "and the severity of a person's illness",
        "start": 186.72,
        "duration": 3.68
    },
    {
        "text": "ultimately the exact numbers on how",
        "start": 188.56,
        "duration": 3.84
    },
    {
        "text": "common this is for covid patients are",
        "start": 190.4,
        "duration": 3.759
    },
    {
        "text": "still unclear but all this seems to",
        "start": 192.4,
        "duration": 4.24
    },
    {
        "text": "suggest that myocarditis may not be",
        "start": 194.159,
        "duration": 3.921
    },
    {
        "text": "related to how sick a person",
        "start": 196.64,
        "duration": 4.4
    },
    {
        "text": "appears and it may be hard to spot and",
        "start": 198.08,
        "duration": 4.32
    },
    {
        "text": "one group of people who may be",
        "start": 201.04,
        "duration": 2.479
    },
    {
        "text": "especially at risk",
        "start": 202.4,
        "duration": 3.199
    },
    {
        "text": "are athletes or anyone who works their",
        "start": 203.519,
        "duration": 3.601
    },
    {
        "text": "heart really hard and there are a few",
        "start": 205.599,
        "duration": 3.2
    },
    {
        "text": "reasons for that for one there's some",
        "start": 207.12,
        "duration": 3.44
    },
    {
        "text": "evidence that exercise could increase",
        "start": 208.799,
        "duration": 3.921
    },
    {
        "text": "inflammation or increase how quickly the",
        "start": 210.56,
        "duration": 3.84
    },
    {
        "text": "virus replicates but there's also the",
        "start": 212.72,
        "duration": 3.519
    },
    {
        "text": "fact that the extra strain athletes put",
        "start": 214.4,
        "duration": 2.72
    },
    {
        "text": "on their hearts can",
        "start": 216.239,
        "duration": 2.64
    },
    {
        "text": "increase their risk of triggering an",
        "start": 217.12,
        "duration": 3.52
    },
    {
        "text": "arrhythmia or heart failure",
        "start": 218.879,
        "duration": 3.521
    },
    {
        "text": "well after the infection experts have",
        "start": 220.64,
        "duration": 3.519
    },
    {
        "text": "long said that if an athlete gets",
        "start": 222.4,
        "duration": 3.919
    },
    {
        "text": "myocarditis from any virus",
        "start": 224.159,
        "duration": 3.681
    },
    {
        "text": "they should be pulled from playing for",
        "start": 226.319,
        "duration": 3.361
    },
    {
        "text": "at least three to six months",
        "start": 227.84,
        "duration": 3.84
    },
    {
        "text": "and pass in exercise tests before",
        "start": 229.68,
        "duration": 3.759
    },
    {
        "text": "resuming competitive sports and",
        "start": 231.68,
        "duration": 3.199
    },
    {
        "text": "depending on what scientists learn in",
        "start": 233.439,
        "duration": 2.401
    },
    {
        "text": "the coming months",
        "start": 234.879,
        "duration": 2.72
    },
    {
        "text": "athletes may not be the only ones who",
        "start": 235.84,
        "duration": 3.28
    },
    {
        "text": "should take extra precautions",
        "start": 237.599,
        "duration": 3.041
    },
    {
        "text": "it may be important to monitor the",
        "start": 239.12,
        "duration": 3.759
    },
    {
        "text": "hearts of everyone who contracts kova 19",
        "start": 240.64,
        "duration": 4.239
    },
    {
        "text": "to check for myocarditis if a person",
        "start": 242.879,
        "duration": 3.761
    },
    {
        "text": "does have it doctors can try to treat",
        "start": 244.879,
        "duration": 3.841
    },
    {
        "text": "the inflammation directly with oxygen or",
        "start": 246.64,
        "duration": 4.159
    },
    {
        "text": "medications they can also warn a person",
        "start": 248.72,
        "duration": 4.0
    },
    {
        "text": "to temporarily avoid activities like",
        "start": 250.799,
        "duration": 3.201
    },
    {
        "text": "sports that might endanger",
        "start": 252.72,
        "duration": 2.799
    },
    {
        "text": "their heart that could be a lifesaver",
        "start": 254.0,
        "duration": 3.199
    },
    {
        "text": "for people who might not have even known",
        "start": 255.519,
        "duration": 3.601
    },
    {
        "text": "they were unwell until it was too late",
        "start": 257.199,
        "duration": 2.961
    },
    {
        "text": "but for now there's still",
        "start": 259.12,
        "duration": 2.959
    },
    {
        "text": "a lot we don't know like if there's a",
        "start": 260.16,
        "duration": 3.84
    },
    {
        "text": "pattern to the symptoms or how long they",
        "start": 262.079,
        "duration": 4.001
    },
    {
        "text": "last while kovid's toll on the heart",
        "start": 264.0,
        "duration": 4.16
    },
    {
        "text": "isn't the most obvious of its symptoms",
        "start": 266.08,
        "duration": 3.76
    },
    {
        "text": "it's one we may need to pay a lot more",
        "start": 268.16,
        "duration": 2.479
    },
    {
        "text": "attention to",
        "start": 269.84,
        "duration": 2.96
    },
    {
        "text": "as we learn more about how to cope with",
        "start": 270.639,
        "duration": 3.041
    },
    {
        "text": "this disease",
        "start": 272.8,
        "duration": 2.08
    },
    {
        "text": "thanks for watching this episode of",
        "start": 273.68,
        "duration": 3.04
    },
